642
00:32:53,169 --> 00:32:54,637
Teško Erol Flin, zar ne?

643
00:32:54,671 --> 00:32:56,606
Pitam se ko je više ljut
na njega trenutno.

644
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:58,241
Njegova žena zbog izdaje

645
00:32:58,276 --> 00:33:00,854
